high_descs: Turn and go to the dresser.
Pick up a pen on the dresser.
Turn and go to the dresser.
Put the pen on the plate on the dresser.
Pick up the plate on the dresser.
Go to the stand by the armchair.
Put the plate on the stand.
anns.task_desc: Move a plate from the dresser to the stand.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the dresser on the far side of the room.
Pick up the pen off of the dresser.
Look up towards the mirror.
Put the pen in the glass bowl on the dresser.
Pick up the glass bowl with the pen in it off of the dresser.
Turn right and walk towards the door, then hang a right and walk over to the small end table to the left of the chair in the corner of the room.
Put the glass bowl on the end table to the right of the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass bowl with a pen in it on an end table.

high_descs: Turn to the left, and then left again to go past the bed and to the dresser.
Pick up the pen from the front of the dresser.
Hold the pen and look up to the mirror.
Place the pen in the bowl to the back of the dresser.
Pick up the bowl from the back of the dresser.
Carry the bowl and turn to the right and then right again past the bed. Find the small table on the left side.
Place the bowl and pen on the small black table, to the right side.
anns.task_desc: Move a bowl and pen to a small table.
